<br>
The way its written and ment to be read, is as such:<br>
<br>
&quot;Does my DEX cause me to Proc a weapon more?&quot; and abashis answer was &quot;The proc rates are a percentage chance modified by dexterity, the type of weapon (1H vs 2H), and the delay rating on the weapon&quot;<br>
<br>
Weapon procs themselves, have different levels of aggro. For sure, and without a doubt.<br>
<br>
The nerf related in article two, was verant (WAY overdue I might add) toning down the aggro level on Spells like Tash line, and other VERY high taunt spells (slow, large nukes etc). As well as toning down the proc level across all spell lines. This is why Furor for so long used 2 Jsticks over even epics after he got them. Untill the nerf &gt;&lt;<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;We reduced the amount of hate that can be caused by a proc. Due to the high proc rates at upper levels, the amount of hate generated from procs, and the spells that were selected for those procs, made keeping the attention of the creature much too easy a task for the tank. Simply, it nearly eliminated the challenge of keeping a foes attention at levels above 50.&quot;<br>
<br>
Why they said this, then made MT strategy the ONLY way to survive the high end game, still to this DAY boggles my mind...<br>
It makes the uber game more about who can chain heal the longest without a fizzle or LD...<br>
<br>
blah, I rant too much. all I should of said was &quot;way to contradict yourself verant!!&quot; <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=28222><img src=http://pages.sprint.ca/gilimi/files/EQ000002.jpg></a></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugilimisilverwing.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilimi Silverwing</A> at: 2/14/02 8:18:22 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=1811.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=1811.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1811.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=1811.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=1811.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1811.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1811.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum m